body:
`count` has the following syntax:

```json
{
  "$searchMeta"|"$search": {
    "index": "<index name>", // optional, defaults to "default"
    "<operator>": {
      <operator-specifications>
    },
    "count": {
      "type": "lowerBound"|"total",
      "threshold": <number-of-documents> //optional
    }
  }
}
```
